  "text": "Baştug et. al. [CITATION_1] show that the information demand patterns of mobile users are predictable to an extent and propose to proactively pre-cache the desirable information before users request it. The social relations and device-to-device communications are leveraged. Fog computing is a much more broad and generic paradigm as compared to [CITATION_2] ; the proactive caching framework described in [CITATION_3] can be applied in Fog computing.",
